shadow: Whether the text has a shadow. (default: false) Not to be confused with an entity shadow.
opacity: The alpha opacity of the text from 0 to 255. (default: 255)
blockdata: A blockdata array (or optionally string) for the block to be displayed.
linewidth: The max width for a line of text before splitting. (default: 200)
alignment: The text alignment. Can be CENTER (default), LEFT or RIGHT.
itemdisplay: The item display model transform to use. Can be FIRSTPERSON_LEFTHAND, FIRSTPERSON_RIGHTHAND, FIXED, GROUND, GUI, HEAD, NONE, THIRDPERSON_LEFTHAND, or THIRDPERSON_RIGHTHAND.
